summary: This document is an investigative subpoena issued by the Town of Palm Beach Police Department, requesting flight records from Jet Aviation related to a criminal investigation involving unlawful sexual activity with minors. The subpoena specifically requests information on two aircraft tail numbers for the year 2005.

persons.name: Daliah Weiss
persons.context: Daliah Weiss is the author of the investigative subpoena related to the criminal investigation.

persons.name: Norbert Enrich
persons.context: Norbert Enrich is mentioned as the point of contact at Jet Aviation for the subpoena request.

locations: 1513 Perimeter Road, West Palm Beach, Florida
345 South County Road, Palm Beach, Florida
keyFacts: The subpoena is part of a criminal investigation into unlawful sexual activity with minors.
The subpoena requests flight records for two specific aircraft tail numbers, N908JE and N909JE.
The document is dated December 29, 2005, and is addressed to Jet Aviation.
